Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.07,0:00:05.13,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Scientist Chen Hung Dao.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.38,0:00:07.52,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Astronaut Christopher Bartholomew.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.55,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Astronaut Eirand Hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:12.07,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Engineer Hubert Heim.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:14.74,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Engineer Leonov Norstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:17.07,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Assistant Navigator James Biko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:20.52,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And next to him are EVA specialist\NSally Silverstone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:24.06,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and fellow EVA specialist Hoshino Hachirota.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:28.28,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,These 18 men and women are the\NVon Braun's handpicked crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.89,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,These are the best of the best, culled from a pool...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:33.51,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...of some 20,000 applicants over a period of eight months.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:37.09,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With their selection, the crew of the Von Braun is now complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:41.02,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To have the honor of introducing crew members of their caliber to you today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:44.68,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...as the first humans to challenge Jupiter fills me with joy that I can hardly contain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:48.24,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Jovian system development project that they will be undertaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:51.27,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...will spur humanity's development to new heights,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:54.57,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and I am sure that tales of their great deeds will be handed down to future generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:00:58.15,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hachimaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:00:59.10,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hachimaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:00.31,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hachimaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:05.00,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop spacing out!\N A reporter is asking you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:07.11,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll repeat the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:10.38,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any worries at all over this long journey of seven years to Jupiter,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:11.94,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...a planet where no one has gone before?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:20.69,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:24.04,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can we assume that it's because of your father that you decided to go to Jupiter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:27.88,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go? Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:31.25,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:37.37,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's jokes aren't very funny, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:42.33,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our biggest worry on this project is that we'll have to listen to his jokes for seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:26.75,F.O. (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(630,368,480,355)\fad(760,830)\bord0.1\shad2\fs20\fscx100\fscy100\t(\fs28\fscx100\fscy100)}The Lost
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:21.96,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Hachimaki, I wish you wouldn't say weird stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:23.96,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gala occasions like that don't happen every day, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.06,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've been acting funny ever since the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:28.15,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you shouldn't go see the doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:29.96,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've passed all my medical checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:32.54,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your body I'm worried about. It's, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.63,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, our first vacation in ages is gonna start tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:36.31,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go have yourself a good time before you come back, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:39.17,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, try to have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:49.05,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I can't believe how far the repairs have come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.71,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...even though it's only been six months since the Space Defense Front attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.94,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Galileo Development worked themselves to the bone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.14,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to have it ready before the crew's debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.96,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That President Dolf of theirs is a real piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:06.15,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?\NCheck it out, it's a bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:09.27,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who brought them on board?\NWe'd better contact the sanitation department.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:12.58,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, and here I thought I could kiss bugs goodbye for a whole seven years...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.93,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with the quarantine procedures around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:21.68,F.O. (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-4\fnMachineScript\b1\fs19\bord0\shad0\move(540,270,275,270)\c&H8F89D3&}Congratulations to Hometown Astronauts\NGoro and Hoshino Hachirota!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.10,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshino-san, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:29.64,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness... I'm used to seeing things like that for my husband, but not my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.12,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, what're you gonna do on your vacation, Sally?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:40.22,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:43.45,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... I'm gonna go back to Earth and have a picnic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:44.72,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A picnic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.06,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, on the bank of the Thames.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.48,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'd never guess it from your face, but you've got a girlish side...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:50.92,Alternative (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leonov!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:54.42,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a celebrity now, so watch what you say and do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:55.51,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.41,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Leo! Have you seen my son around?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:02.13,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Hachi, he came here on the flight before ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.60,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I should've known...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:07.17,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd that kid go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:19.99,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute. They said to put those files in the folder on the server for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:22.11,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we going to transmit them to Technora?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:26.55,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,President Dolf's orders. I don't know the details, but it's probably a security issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.57,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, all these complicated procedures are getting out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:33.37,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I bet President Dolf is the only one who has access to all the information...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:36.28,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An O   depletion alarm? From a spacesuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:36.28,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(160,480)\fs20}2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.79,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't all the crew on vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.75,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The signal's... coming from the lunar surface?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:55.81,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rescue Command, this is Rescue 42.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:57.68,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've found the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:01.71,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rescue Command, this is Rescue 42.\NWe've found the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.22,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is Rescue Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.91,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshino? You're Hoshino Hachirota, right?\N Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:13.80,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:14.71,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.78,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been doing out here for two days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:21.84,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, if you hadn't been wearing one of the\NVon Braun's custom suits, you'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.55,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.91,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let me replenish your O  .
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.91,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(550,480)\fs20}2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.57,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Open up the cartridge on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:33.94,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When we get back, I'm sending you in for a complete checkup, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.91,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get back? Back where? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:46.21,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Cheng-Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:50.20,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't carried passengers in a while, so make sure you're good and nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.83,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:56.90,Other (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for choosing to fly with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:07:00.95,Other (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We ask that our passengers follow the following rules while we are en route.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:03.73,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President!\NWhere are the Hoshinos?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.18,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I sent them back to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.90,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshino Hachirota is in need of R&R.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.31,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then you could have sent the son by himself, couldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:11.75,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The father didn't need to go with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:13.77,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was a request from the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.51,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshino Hachirota wanted to continue with his training,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.08,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but Hoshino Goro said that he would take him back to Earth personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:26.83,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Dr. Locksmith, there is another matter that I'd like to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.82,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? You look awfully serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:32.33,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you'll have to forgive me, but it's an important matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.89,Other (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our flight has been delayed due to schedule adjustments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.86,Other (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our departure will be one hour behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.73,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me? Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:47.05,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've got an hour layover before our connecting flight... You hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:51.33,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And here we are, two celebrities who have to travel incognito...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:51.72,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:57.94,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, I know!\NI'll go buy us something to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:00.79,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi, what do you want?\NSome sake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.20,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're on!\NYou better keep up with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:03.86,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:09.12,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Technora!\NWhich way do I go to get to Technora?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:12.36,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To reach Technora, please use the elevator that's four blocks ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.91,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and take it to the business floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.20,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can find their reception desk there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.11,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Four blocks ahead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:28.87,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:51.78,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Tanabe's still using this desk after all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:53.28,F.O. (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-60\frx15\fnNew Dr. Yoshiabibi\fs26\c&H000218&\bord0\shad0\pos(300,276)}Last Will
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:53.41,F.O. (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-65\fnNew Dr. Yoshiabibi\fs26\c&H000218&\bord0\shad0\pos(348,244)}Last Will
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:53.53,F.O. (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-65\fnNew Dr. Yoshiabibi\fs28\c&H000218&\bord0\shad0\pos(375,228)}Last Will
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:53.66,F.O. (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-65\fnNew Dr. Yoshiabibi\fs28\c&H000218&\bord0\shad0\pos(402,211)}Last Will
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:53.78,F.O. (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-65\fnNew Dr. Yoshiabibi\fs28\c&H000218&\bord0\shad0\pos(445,195)}Last Will
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:53.91,F.O. (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-65\fnNew Dr. Yoshiabibi\fs28\c&H000218&\bord0\shad0\pos(493,187)}Last Will
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:53.95,F.O. (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-63\fnNew Dr. Yoshiabibi\fs30\c&H000218&\bord0\shad0\pos(585,170)}Last Will
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:57.62,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, what did I write in my own will?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:08:59.62,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be! It's Ha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.40,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you were coming, you should've let us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.76,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing, Hachi!\NI saw you on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.86,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've really made something of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:09.76,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Wait here, I'll call\NFee-kun and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.24,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they at the union meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:11.77,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:15.37,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See, ever we lost Claire-san and Tanabe-kun, we've been awfully shorthanded around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:16.94,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She left?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:19.38,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:21.13,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:23.91,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tanabe-kun went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.22,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Back to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:29.59,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ai-chan went through a lot of things, and she ended up resigning from the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:30.53,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.49,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, she's still young!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:35.70,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She can always start again from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:40.44,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here are Tanabe-kun's address and phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:45.30,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She pretended that everything was okay, but she wanted to go see you, Ha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:47.76,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go pay her a visit before you leave for Jupiter. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.42,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,182 centimeters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:23.88,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, that works out to an average of... um, 1.75cm a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:26.13,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're growing like a weed, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:29.03,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Show a little more consideration for the Earth when you're living down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.32,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or more to the point, quit eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:32.32,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take those pork cutlets off your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:37.19,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not making any sense, old man.\N You should be happy that your son is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.59,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're growing too big, is my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.29,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Hachi.\NYou should eat up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:43.19,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to have these for the next seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.47,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to let Kyu have 'em all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.85,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi quit growing a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:50.68,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And while we're at it, don't act like hot stuff just 'cause you're going to Jupiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:55.10,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By the time you two get back from Jupiter,\NI'm gonna build a ship to go to Venus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.02,Alternative (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What're you spouting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:58.73,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It was money that I earned that put those pork cutlets on your plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:57.82,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.92,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't eat faster, they'll take them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.12,Alternative (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gee, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.29,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:04.25,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Who do you think you have to thank for growing so big, huh, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:02.95,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:05.38,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:14.73,Other (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Their pitcher, Iketani, had a string of injuries last season.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:13.32,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.67,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno, maybe something did happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:18.80,Other (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Uchida? What's your opinion after seeing the season this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:16.87,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.82,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:22.70,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I thought he had that bug that sailors always catch that's like the measles,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.01,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...so I let him be, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:25.93,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Will he be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:31.11,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd thought he might snap out of it if he had some of your pork cutlets, but, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:35.07,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:38.29,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wonder what happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:54.71,F.O. (PlanetES),,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-69\fnNew Dr. Yoshiabibi\fs20\c&H000218&\bord0\shad0\move(546,268,550,262)\t(\fs22)}Last Will
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:56.56,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oops. I accidentally left the office with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:06.25,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just gonna have a bunch of stuff about "love" in it, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:12.44,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-18\fry-20\fs22\b1\fnNew Dr. Yoshiabibi\bord0\shad0\c&H141414&\move(535,350,525,340)\t(\fs24)}Last Will
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.69,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Tanabe, I just started here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:13:00.49,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a diaper man like you wouldn't understand that, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:01.99,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Senpai!\NLet's see some spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:04.07,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! Senpai, I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.71,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so sorry! I just assumed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:09.45,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're renting a place in\NArnould Area, too, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:11.75,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're my sensei, right, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:14.41,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think this is a time for worrying about who's a rookie or who's a Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.18,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good! Rewrite it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:20.92,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you were rude and violent, but I didn't think you were capable of this, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:23.82,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm saying that you've got no delicacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:26.47,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave them love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:31.20,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that will you wrote!\NYou're the one with the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:34.94,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you understand?!\NWe can't send this man back into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:37.61,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that at all!\NI was worried that you might...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:40.40,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.45,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are they shooting out? Of my eyes, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:45.80,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your turn, Senpai.\NI told you, so now you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:46.75,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's a simple reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.57,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's your style.\NIt's just what you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:52.48,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How is he?!\NIs he going to be all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.91,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness... I'm so relieved...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:57.92,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:00.58,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:03.57,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much that I want to ask you and talk to you about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:08.12,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You decided all on your own to quit the company and to try out for the Von Braun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:12.88,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to tell me about it.\NTo talk to me about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:20.14,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you aren't having second thoughts, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:25.11,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're weak. You're still trying to turn to others for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:29.61,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, didn't I?\NIn the end, all humans are alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:35.77,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess I am. I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.23,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really alone, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:41.75,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.70,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:08.62,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:11.33,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing... Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:13.84,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Am I dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:18.69,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:20.32,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one thing I'm sure of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:22.47,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:26.14,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here... I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:28.08,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:32.66,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, that's exactly what I said, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.62,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I wanted, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:37.10,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:40.98,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not here... Not like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:42.13,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:44.70,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:01.79,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, this is what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:06.21,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, and fall into the abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.97,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:11.93,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shoot, and then I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.26,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No ammo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:22.02,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hakim! Don't act like you know it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:35.45,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My determination wasn't all talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.18,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I really did intend to put an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:40.69,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I really intended to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:42.05,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:44.41,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,the gun didn't fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:48.28,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I pulled the trigger, but the gun didn't fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:51.20,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:53.80,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whose is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:59.59,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault? No, what do I have to thank for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:03.59,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do I owe my thanks to for not having to shoot him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:06.20,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:08.70,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Senpai, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:12.38,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tanabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.62,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:24.64,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What're you waiting for, dummy Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.30,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Hachimaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.01,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave you to it, Ha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:31.59,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi, didn't I tell you that nobody gets overtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:32.75,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's quitting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:34.64,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You never change, do you, Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:35.97,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can do it, Hachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:37.40,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Hachimaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:38.98,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hachimaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:45.01,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take it nice and easy, there's no rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.07,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, you dumb kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:50.16,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act big when your job's not done yet, nii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:51.71,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi, the food will all be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:28.23,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:30.10,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was space?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:35.77,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If what I just saw was space, then what the hell have I been looking at up until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:44.44,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:55.57,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:57.68,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hachimaki Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.35,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:03.22,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:12.16,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have my dad go get your bike later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:13.93,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:18.41,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me. I went all the way to the Von Braun to see you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:21.12,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the ship's off-limits to unauthorized personnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:24.40,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I cheated a little.\NI asked Colin-san to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:27.11,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Colin? You mean that idiot son of the INTO chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.81,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He says he works for INTO as an inspector now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:34.61,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just as we were asking them to call for you,\N we got caught up in that big mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:35.59,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:37.44,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tanabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:41.04,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your legs didn't get hurt in the\NSpace Defense Front attack, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:44.90,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, I escaped right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:49.29,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the place where I came down was too far away from a manned facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:50.87,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What about an SOS?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.42,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I sent one out, but nobody answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:56.80,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have any choice, so I started to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.30,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But my O   ran out on the way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.30,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,480)\fs20}2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:00.71,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:01.32,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:04.36,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was rescued by a shuttle bus that happened to be passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.88,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I suffered nerve damage from the oxygen deprivation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:11.54,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and I underwent a tricky procedure called a "nano nerve coupler" operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:16.19,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I remembered the medical lingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:18.98,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was out here doing my rehabilitation exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:22.93,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The doctors say that if I work hard at it,\NI'll make a full recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:24.62,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They did, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:25.58,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.58,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Claire-san was discharged from the hospital right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:29.60,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Claire?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:32.30,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. She escaped from the ship with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:36.28,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she had been using a lot less O   than I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:36.28,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,480)\fs20}2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.65,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There was less damage to her brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:42.21,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It sounded to me like my rehabilitation would take a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:46.15,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and since I didn't even know if I'd recover,\NI submitted a letter of resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:47.88,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:48.83,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:51.92,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:03.95,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tanabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:07.96,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's something that\NI need to apologize to you for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:13.19,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I read this without asking.\NSo I thought I should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:18.44,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:24.80,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote out a proper will last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:30.18,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It said stuff like "Thank you for raising me,"\N and "Goodbye," and "I'm sorry"...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:34.74,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They told me to write out another one this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:40.17,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but after all the things I'd experienced firsthand out in space, and with you gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:42.66,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I couldn't write anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:46.08,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And after all those things I said to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:49.96,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing that I wrote felt right to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:53.18,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:21:59.07,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tanabe... When we ran into each other a minute ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:00.48,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I think I figured something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.29,0:22:04.91,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My idea of space was too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.89,0:22:09.88,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, there's a lot of painful stuff and questions without answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:14.96,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but there's nothing in this world that isn't part of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:19.62,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that even I'm connected to it.\N That those connections are what make up space.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.39,0:22:25.00,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that maybe I'm okay with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:28.07,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:31.89,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that's what you were trying to tell me, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:34.61,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That everything in this world is connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:38.55,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And the thing that binds it all together is...
